{"tid":1853901,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Marvel《尚氣》男主角為武漢打氣“病毒不會分裂我們，恐懼和偏見才會”","createTime":"2020-01-31T08:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T04:45:27.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":156,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"69689fece8e1bf5e8dd05ec254c33b6eb061821c","tid":1853901,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:35:10.000Z","msg":"今日，漫威《尚氣》男主角劉思慕在社交媒體發文稱&ldquo;病毒不會分裂我們，恐懼和偏見才會&rdquo;，並配上一張武漢的圖片，為武漢人民打氣。<br />\n<br />\n武漢疫情爆發後，國外社交媒體上出現了一些帶有歧視性的評論。作為一名華裔演員，劉思慕此前就曾在社交平台上發文，稱部分媒體對中國新型冠狀病毒的報導存在雙重標準，&ldquo;新型冠狀病毒不是你往亞洲人身上潑髒水的理由&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n 劉思慕1989年出生於中國黑龍江省哈爾濱市，是一名加拿大華裔演員。他將在漫威2021年的新片《尚氣》中飾演男主角。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6mgkRNT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6mgkRNT.jpg&h=1a97e6dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90a837cf7ce980b4f26db9024530264f882ddce7","tid":1853901,"uid":70800,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:37:05.000Z","msg":"外國勢力"},{"pid":"311b6bac7959a3fed63d5b8a40fe36ccae0fa2dd","tid":1853901,"uid":112316,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:37:50.000Z","msg":"加拿大華裔演員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025b2686b91c57bb9c0cff4feb5dd50616aa0a7a","tid":1853901,"uid":55533,"like":37,"dislike":9,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"睇mcu既都係垃圾"},{"pid":"5d71dcb808624bab59ae338d5575821300bb5e78","tid":1853901,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:39:41.000Z","msg":"柒頭"},{"pid":"a0e3adf1f43c50bdc33194649585df9e6ad40350","tid":1853901,"uid":149844,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:40:57.000Z","msg":"雙重國籍個啲可以放棄定支那戶籍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡稱集團叛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52dc8b09fc179e1e067da057c09a3d10391457aa","t